==Mandarin==
[[Pinyin]]: yī shí èr niǎo

===Etymology===
Literally: one stone, two birds

===Idiom===
# [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals

===Synonyms===
*[[一箭双雕]]
*[[一举两得]]

